<button class="structure__features-btn text-base collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse-02" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="heading-02">

А в блоке выпадашки убрать класс show

<div id="collapse-02" aria-labelledby="heading-02" data-bs-parent="#structureFeatures" class="structure__features-collpase text-sm collapse">

